      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "text": "PREDICT — every move (odometry / IMU)\nμ' = f(μ, u)        move the guess forward\nP' = F·P·F^T + Q    GROW uncertainty (+Q)",
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "predict",
      "originalText": "PREDICT — every move (odometry / IMU)\nμ' = f(μ, u)        move the guess forward\nP' = F·P·F^T + Q    GROW uncertainty (+Q)",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
