      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "text": "UPDATE — when a measurement arrives\nK = P'·H^T·(H·P'·H^T + R)^-1     trust dial\nμ = μ' + K·(z − h(μ'))          slide to measurement\nP = (I − K·H)·P'                 SHRINK uncertainty",
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "update",
      "originalText": "UPDATE — when a measurement arrives\nK = P'·H^T·(H·P'·H^T + R)^-1     trust dial\nμ = μ' + K·(z − h(μ'))          slide to measurement\nP = (I − K·H)·P'                 SHRINK uncertainty",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
